mapping)", "investigate unmapped finding F-005
(unmapped_reason: no_osc_r_category_for_cwe)") based on real
evidence — not speculative.

OCAP BOUNDARY (P4): Metric computed from mapping evidence only;
no external taxonomy database download; no ambient scanning.

CNS REGULATION (P9): `cns.taxonomy.convergence` emitted
